channel.title: Task 1: Setting Up the Starter Code :: Introduction to Web Dev
channel.description: Fork and clone the starter code repository . To get started, navigate to the directory with your copy of the starter code. Run npm install. Open index.html with Firefox to verify that your starter code is working. When you open index.html in the browser, you should see the Launch Checklist form with a rectangle above it for the mission destination and a rectangle below it that simply says “Awaiting Information Before Launch”.
